      "role": "user",
      "content": "a gatekeeper lol okay. so is the reactance just like a constant pushback or does it fluctuate? i'm trying to visualize why it behaves differently than a regular resistor.",
      "source": "evaluator",
      "targeted_response_start": "",
      "beast_baseline": "a gatekeeper lol okay. so is the reactance just like a constant pushback or does it fluctuate? i'm trying to visualize why it behaves differently than a regular resistor.",
